nl.tue.geometrycore.geometry

Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tue.geometrycore.geometry.BaseGeometry<Vector>
      • nl.tue.geometrycore.geometry.Vector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeometryConvertable<Vector>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DCELVertex, SimpleVertex

    public class Vector
extends BaseGeometry<Vector>
    This class is used to represent a 2-dimensional point or vector in Euclidean space.
